const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What Instagram account type do I need?",
    answer: "Covered in your onboarding — we guide you through the free switch to a Business or Creator account on your phone, then connect the DM channel from our end. The entire process takes a couple of minutes and requires zero technical knowledge from you. Fire protection companies producing visual documentation of fire stopping, intumescent coatings, and sprinkler installations commonly operate Business accounts already for the content promotion features."
  },
  {
    question: "What fire protection DMs come through Instagram?",
    answer: "Building management professionals, developers, and construction industry contacts who follow fire safety content. Typical DMs include 'we need compartmentation surveys across our portfolio — are you FIRAS?', 'can you quote for an alarm upgrade to L1?', and 'our fire doors need replacing — do you supply FD30 and FD60?' These leads convert reliably because the sender has already seen evidence of your certification and workmanship."
  },
  {
    question: "How fast does the AI respond to fire protection DMs?",
    answer: "Within seconds of receipt. Instagram shows read indicators, so the building professional sees your company engaging immediately. When a Responsible Person is messaging three fire protection firms under enforcement pressure, the first company to respond with pertinent questions about the building type and deficiency scope typically secures the survey."
  },
  {
    question: "What does Instagram DMs cost for fire protection companies?",
    answer: `Instagram DMs is available at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month as a channel add-on. Fire protection companies with strong visual portfolios — showing certified fire stopping installations, intumescent steelwork projects, and sprinkler commissioning — attract high-value compliance enquiries. A single multi-block remediation contract secured through a prompt Instagram DM starts at £20,000 and can exceed £150,000.`
  },
  {
    question: "Can I reply to DMs personally?",
    answer: "Send a message in any DM thread and the AI transfers control to you permanently. It recognises your response and withdraws. Most fire protection specialists let the AI gather the essentials — building type, fire discipline, deficiency scope, certification requirement, compliance timeline — then take over to discuss methodology, share case studies, and schedule the survey."
  },
